<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Wilhelm II., Markgraf von Meißen</head><p>Der Rat bittet erneut um Freilassung des gefangenen Christian Haller, Sohn des Peter Haller, Bürger und Ratsherr zu Nürnberg.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_45" id="21v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_45_r1l1">Marggraf VVılhelm </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_45_r1l2">von Meihſen </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_45_r1l3">Gnediger <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> . Als vvir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>fürſtenlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gnaden nehſt <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_45_r1l4"> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / 
<del rend="strikethrough">Als </del> von Criſtan Hallers des peter Hallers <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>lıeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>burg<ex>er</ex>s</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_45_r1l6">vnd Ratgeſellen ſuns wegen / Alſo hat vns der <expan>egen<ex>ante</ex></expan> ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> Ratgeſelle </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_45_r1l9"> <expan>yecʒund<ex>en</ex></expan> fürbraht / vvie der <expan>egen<ex>ante</ex></expan> ſein Sun noch 
<add><ab facs="#facs_45_line_1577009906372_1616">
<del rend="strikethrough">etwaʒ </del> gen <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> behafft </ab></add>
<del rend="strikethrough"> ſwerlich in ewrn <expan>vngnade<ex>n</ex></expan></del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_45_r1l10">ſey . 
<del rend="strikethrough">Alſo daʒ Jm ſölich vnſer bete vnd <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> biʒ her gen ewrer </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_45_r1l11">
<del rend="strikethrough">hochwirdıkeit niht cʒeſtaten kumen ſey </del> . Vnd wan vvir doch allcʒeit </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_45_r1l12">cʒu <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>fürſtenlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gnaden gut cʒuverſiht vnd <expan>getrawe<ex>n</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> gehabt </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_45_r1l13">
<del rend="strikethrough">vnd auch noch </del> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . vns vnd den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> gnad vnd <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> cʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_45_r1l14">beweiſen . Hyrümb biten vvir ewr <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> aber <expan>dinſtlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mit allem </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_45_r1l15">fleiſʒ . daʒ Jr 
<del rend="strikethrough">ſölch vngnad gen </del> des <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> burgers ſun vmb <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_45_r1l18">willigen dinſte vvillen 
<add><ab facs="#facs_45_line_1577009923598_1636">
<del rend="strikethrough">darümb </del></ab></add>
<del rend="strikethrough"> varen vnd Jn </del> <expan>gnediklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von euch <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> laſſen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_45_r1l19">wöllet . Alſo daʒ Er <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> bete darynne gen <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>fürſtenlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gnaden </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_45_r1l20">genyſſe . Als vvir des <expan>denſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden wol getrawen . Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_45_r1l21">vvir v̈mb <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> vnd dy <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> williklich vnd gern <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dienen</expan> . <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_45_r1l23"><expan>fe<ex>r</ex>ia</expan> vj̃ <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Oſwaldi Anno etc xix<hi rend="sup">no</hi> . </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_45" id="21v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Marggraf Wilhelm von Meihsen </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Gnediger <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürstenlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gnaden nehst
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von Cristan Hallers, des Peter Hallers
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>s</expan> und ratgesellen suns wegen, also hat uns der
                                <expan>egen<ex>ante</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> ratgeselle <expan>yeczund<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        fürbraht, wie der <expan>egen<ex>ante</ex></expan> sein sun noch <add>gen
                                    <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> behafft</add> sey. Und wan wir
                        doch allczeit czu <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürstenlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gnaden gut czuversiht und
                                <expan>getrawe<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, uns und den <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
                        gnad und <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> czu beweisen, hyrümb biten wir ewr
                                <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> aber
                                <expan>dinstlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mit allem fleisz, daz ir des
                                <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan> burgers sun umb
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> willigen dinste willen
                                <expan>gnediklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von euch
                            <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> lassen wöllet. Also daz er
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> bete darynne gen
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürstenlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gnaden genysse, als wir des
                                <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden wol getrawen. Das
                            <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir ümb <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> und dy <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
                        williklich und gern <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dienen</expan>.
                            <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>r</ex>ia</expan> vi <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Oswaldi anno
                        etc. xix<hi rend="sup">no</hi>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
